title: BONUS SESH: Jessi Klein and the Sha-rrest!!!
description: Bonus Ep! Casey and Danielleare in DEEP conversation with comedian, writer, Emmy winner and hilarious human Jessi Klein about talismans motherhood and her new bookI'll Show Myself Out. Plus breaking news about Jen Shah's guilty plea hits the airwaves and Casey andDanielleare Sha-shocked!!!!! And Sha-ooketh!!!!!
